FBIS3-22915 "jptot008__l94015" JPRS-TOT-94-008-L Document Type:JPRS Document Title:Terrorism FOUO 1 March 1994 AFRICA SOUTH AFRICA Gunmen Kill Azapo Official in Soweto 13 Feb MB1402080894 Johannesburg Radio South Africa Network in English 0500 GMT 14 Feb 94 MB1402080894 Johannesburg Radio South Africa Network Language: English Article Type:BFN [Text] A leading member of the Azanian People's Liberation Army [Azapo], Mr. Letsatsi Mosala, has been shot dead by unknown gunmen in Soweto, near Johannesburg. Mr. Mosala, a member of Azapo's strategy committee and a former national organizer for the organization, was shot at point blank range while driving through the Rockville area of Soweto last night. The gunmen escaped in his car.
